# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:295
msgid ""
"**Keep Both Sides**: This option splits the clip into two parts, keeping "
"everything on both sides of the play-head. It’s useful when you want to "
"break a clip into sections but don’t want to remove anything."
msgstr ""
"**Halda báðum hliðum**: Þessi valkostur skiptir klipinu í tvær einingar og "
"heldur öllu á báðum hliðum spilunarhausins. Hann er gagnlegur þegar þú vilt "
"skipta klipi í hluta en vilt ekki fjarlægja neitt."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:296
msgid ""
"**Keep Left Side**: This option cuts the clip and removes the part to the "
"right of the play-head, keeping only the part before the play-head. Use this "
